title: The Complete Ash vs. Evil Dead Collection (Re Upload)
description:
The most Definitive, The most Complete, ASH VS. EVIL DEAD COLLECTION ever put together here on the bay. Complete with behind the scenes extras, starting with all 3 classic evil dead 80's movies.

By the way, Don't believe what he said, Bruce Campbell isn't retiring, he's just saying that so that the deadites can think that they can roam free, then...BAM!! BREAK OUT THE BOOMSTICK BABY!! 'Cmon yall, who's with me? You wanna be a ghostbeater or not?
